::Spears::

She looked at Striker.
"If there is anything you can do to speed up out flight and get us to 
the ground as soon as possable, I would greatly appreciate it."

she was shaking a little fromt he fear of being high in the air for 
hours.  He told her it would take a few more hours than planned, but 
this was getting to be too much.
